# Project-root .env — gitignored. Copy to .env and fill in real values.
#
# Loaded automatically by `pnpm -C server dev` (via Node's --env-file-if-exists
# flag). For the compiled paths (`pnpm exec ledger`, `node dist/bin/ledger.js`)
# you must either export these variables yourself or run the binary under
# `node --env-file=.env …`.

# Anthropic auth for the agent-dispatcher's `claude --bare` subprocess.
# Required for `06-agent-dispatcher`'s dispatch flow (parent §Acceptance check
# items 3–6). `--bare` strictly requires ANTHROPIC_API_KEY or apiKeyHelper;
# OAuth and keychain are blocked by design.
#
# Two ways to fill this in:
#   1. Subscription-backed (Pro/Max): run `claude setup-token` once interactively,
#      paste the resulting token here. Billing draws from your Claude subscription.
#   2. API-credit: create an API key at https://console.anthropic.com/settings/keys,
#      paste the resulting `sk-ant-…` value here. Billing draws from API credits.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the API server port (default 4180).
# LEDGER_PORT=4180

# Optional: gate the env-gated real-claude smoke test in 03-claude-code-executor
# (off by default; the fake-claude fixture covers the integration path mechanically).
# LEDGER_SMOKE_TESTS=1
